name: Wings of Eagles
about: Wings of Eagles Aviation is a premier flight training institution based in Middle Tennessee, with over 16 years of experience in providing professional flight training. As a FAA-approved 141 flight training facility and an affiliate of Liberty University, we offer a comprehensive range of programs including sport pilot, private pilot certification, instrument rating, multi-engine rating, and commercial pilot certification. Our training includes both single-engine aircraft and simulator sessions, along with additional ground school and seminars. We are committed to helping our students achieve their aviation goals, whether it's transitioning from rotor to fixed-wing aircraft or advancing to commercial flying careers. Our dedicated team of instructors ensures a high standard of training, preparing students for successful careers in aviation. For more information, contact us at 615-355-0033.
